 1980'' || {{lang|zh-Hans|\u604b\u66f21980}} || Zheng Wen|| <ref name=love>{{cite web|url=http://news.mtime.com/2018/09/28/1584676.html|script-title=zh:\u300a\u4e0d\u6210\u95ee\u9898\u7684\u95ee\u9898\u300b\u5bfc\u6f14\u6885\u5cf0\u65b0\u7247\u5408\u4f5c\u6625\u590f \u300a\u604b\u66f21980\u300b\u5728\u4eac\u5f00\u673a \u7537\u4e3b\u89d2\u4e3a\u201c\u6cb3\u795e\u201d\u674e\u73b0|date=September 28, 2018|website=Mtime|language=zh}}</ref> \n|-\n| ''Schemes in Antiques '' || {{lang|zh|\u53e4\u8463\u5c40\u4e2d\u5c40}} || Yao Buran ||\n|}\n\n===Television series===\n{| class=\"wikitable\" \n|-\n! width=10|Year\n! English title\n! Chinese title \n! Role\n! Network\n! Notes/Ref.\n|- \n| 2014 || ''City of Fantasy'' || {{lang|zh-Hans|\u5947\u5999\u4e16\u7eaa}} || Ah Liang || [[Youku]] || \n|-\n|rowspan=3| 2016 ||''Four Ladies'' || {{lang|zh-Hans|\u7fe9\u7fe9\u51b7\u5c11\u4fcf\u4f73\u4eba}} || Ding Zihui ||  Nantong Broadcasting Channel||  <ref>{{cite web|url=http://ent.ifeng.com/a/20180202/43026619_0.shtml|script-title=zh:\u300a\u7fe9\u7fe9\u51b7\u5c11\u4fcf\u4f73\u4eba\u300b2\u67085\u65e5\u5f00\u64ad \u674e\u73b0\u9996\u6f14\u8c6a\u95e8\u6c11\u56fd\u5927\u620f|date=February 2, 2018|website=ifeng|language=zh}}</ref>\n|-\n| ''Who Sleeps My Bro'' || {{lang|zh-Hans|\u7761\u5728\u6211\u4e0a\u94fa\u7684\u5144\u5f1f}} || Xie Xun ||[[LeTV]]||   \n|-\n| ''[[Medical Examiner Dr. Qin]]'' || {{lang|zh-Hans|\u6cd5\u533b\u79e6\u660e}} || Lin Tao || [[Sohu TV]] ||  \n|-\n|rowspan=2| 2017 || ''[[Rush to the Dead Summer (TV series)|Rush to the Dead Summer]]'' || {{lang|zh|\u590f\u81f3\u672a\u81f3}} || Qing Yun || [[Hunan TV]] || Cameo<ref>{{cite web|url=https://news.china.com/news100/11038989/20170708/30940597_all.html|script-title=zh:\u300a\u590f\u81f3\u672a\u81f3\u300b\u674e\u73b0\u966a\u7acb\u590f\u770b\u5c0f\u53f8\u753b\u5c55\uff1a\u559c\u6b22\u5168\u4e70\u4e86\uff0cman\u7206|date=July 8, 2017|website=China.com|language=zh}}</ref> \n|-\n| ''[[Tientsin Mystic]]'' || {{lang|zh|\u6cb3\u795e}