 || \"Hello 2020\" || \u4f60\u597d2020 || || Performance for CCTV Spring Gala<br>with [[Zhu Yilong]], [[Li Qin (actress)|Li Qin]], [[Ma Sichun]] & [[Zhou Dongyu]]<ref>{{cite web|url=https://ent.sina.com.cn/v/m/2020-01-24/doc-iihnzhha4525233.shtml|title=\u9c9c\u8089\u9c9c\u82b1\u9f50\u540c\u6846 \u6731\u4e00\u9f99\u674e\u73b0\u8868\u767d2020|date=January 24, 2020|website=Sina|language=zh}}</ref>\n|-\n| \"Wuhan, How Are You\" || \u6b66\u6c49\uff0c\u4f60\u597d\u5417 || || [[2019\u201320 coronavirus pandemic|corona virus]] Wuhan support song<ref>{{cite news |last1=Qian |first1=Gao |title=Hubei people write, Hubei people sing |url=http://bjwb.bjd.com.cn/html/2020-02/07/content_12445484.htm |accessdate=1 April 2020 |publisher=[[Beijing Evening News]] |date=February 7, 2020 |pages=13 |language=zh |quote=Wuhan, how are you\" written by Wang Pingjiu and composed by Chang Shilei, sung by Zhu Yilong, Li Xian....}}</ref>\n|}\n\n==Awards and nominations==\n{| class=\"wikitable\"\n|-\n! Year\n! Award\n! Category\n! Nominated work\n! Result\n! Ref. \n|- \n|2017\n|Netease Awards\n|Most Popular Actor\n|''[[Tientsin Mystic]]''\n|{{won}} \n|<ref>{{cite web|url=http://news.163.com/17/1123/22/D3V8U5OQ000189DH.html|script-title=zh:vivo X20\u7f51\u6613\u5e74\u5ea6\u6001\u5ea6\u5927\u8d4f\u661f\u5149\u71a0\u71a0 \u4f17\u661f\u8be0\u91ca\"\u6211\u4eec\u90fd\u662f\u53d1\u5149\u4f53\"|date=November 23, 2017|website=Netease|language=zh}}</ref>\n|-\n| rowspan=10|2019\n| GQ 2019 Men of the Year\n| Popular Actor of the Year\n|rowspan=4|''[[Go Go Squid!]]''\n|{{won}}\n|<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.dnycwh.com/news/1302766.html|script-title=zh:\u539f\u521b \u674e\u73b0\u83b7GQ\u5e74\u5ea6\u4eba\u6c14\u6f14\u5458\u5956\uff0c\u6f14\u6280\u8d85\u5f3a\u5b9e\u81f3\u540d\u5f52\uff0c\u662f\u91d1\u5b50\u603b\u4f1a\u53d1\u5149\"|date=September 6, 2019|website=GQ Men of The Year|language=zh}}\n</ref>\n|-\n|6th The Actors of China Award Ceremony\n| Best Actor (Emerald Category)\n|{{nom}}\n|<ref>{{cite web|ur